<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-HK">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>KMB 巴士到站查詢 - GitHub Learning Project 1</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>🚌 九龍巴士 到站查詢</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">GitHub Learning Project 1</p>
        
        <div class="search-box">
            <input type="text" id="routeInput" placeholder="輸入路線號，例如 1A" value="1A">
            <select id="serviceType">
                <option value="1">服務類型 1（正常）</option>
                <option value="2">服務類型 2</option>
            </select>
            <button onclick="searchETA()">🔍 查詢</button>
        </div>

        <div id="result" class="result">
            <!-- 查詢結果會顯示在這裡 -->
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>